    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FLOOR X is an anomaly hunting game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to escape from a surreal office where the space is constantly changing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each floor is like a box of chocolates, you never know what you'll find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some anomalies are easy to spot, some are scary, some are surreal, some are funny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From floor to floor, your challenges and gameplay may change.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay attention to the differences in the office and take pictures of anything unusual that catches your eye.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Surreal Expirience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325310/extras/571f9192aba2ca66f156487586bcc515.poster.avif?t=1757652132\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325310/extras/571f9192aba2ca66f156487586bcc515.webm?t=1757652132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325310/extras/571f9192aba2ca66f156487586bcc515.mp4?t=1757652132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 unique anomalies;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three levels. With each level you will unlock new floors with new anomalies and the difficulty will increase.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Changing game rules depending on the type of anomalies.</p></li></ul>",
